

* Recognize the file-type by extension and/or by content. (See Padre for file-type guessing code)

* Process a Perl file using Regex  (Later see Padre for this)
* Processs a JavaScript file using Regex.
* Process a Python file using Regex.
* Process a Ruby file using Regex.


* The sha1 of the file can be the key in the database.
* Store the
   language
   filename
   project name






* Allow the mapping of specific files to file-types by an external configuration file or maybe even wildcards to file-types mapping.




